Ok, I'm going to be gone for a good 5-8 hours after 12 AM Pacific Time

So, here are my characters that I'm going to give you control of to 
participate in the battle near Vehement's base, unless I say otherwise in an 
IM.


The Oblitercons
Demon Wulf - Optic lasers, sword, blade of sword shoots out as missile, then 
replaced

Flesh Ripper - Plasma rifle, and can form explosive orbs of blue energy in 
hands
Dark Claw - Transforms into attack vehicle mode and fires off missiles and 
lasers
Double Punch - Has cloaking device, and fires energy-signature seeking 
missiles)
Manterror - Ion disks
Injector - Has two stinger missile launchers and optic lasers
Bumblebee - Has two stinger missile launchers and optic lasers
Sixshot - Stay with space fighter or tank mode
Ares - Tank with four cannons that can fire at the same time for a max of 16 
shots.
